<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.4">
<l>eṉakkēyāṭ ceyyek kālattu meṉṟeṉ</l>
<l>maṉakkēvan tiṭaivī ṭiṉṟi maṉṉi</l>
<l>taṉakkē yākave ṉaikoḷḷu mītē</l>
<l>yeṉakkē kaṇṇaṉai yāṉkoḷ ciṟappē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying “be my servant at all times”, coming</l>
<l>to my mind, staying without vacating the place</l>
<l>he takes me to be just his. This</l>
<l>is the exultation I take [to be] Kṛṣṇa for me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
